===Small caliber Main guns update===
*[[12.7cm Twin Gun Mount Model B Kai 2]], [[12.7cm Twin Gun Mount Model C Kai 2]] and [[12.7cm Twin Gun Mount Model D Kai 2]] now give additional stats when used on certain ships and ship classes.
===[[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]] update===
